#Text=Israeli-Palestinian conflict : Day 20
#Text=Thursday , January 15 , 2009
#Text=Contribute to Wikinews by expanding these briefs or add a new one .
#Text=A compilation of brief news reports on the Israeli-Palestinian conflict : Day 20
#Text=Hamas agrees to outlines of ceasefire brokered by Egypt , heavy fighting continues
#Text=Map of the Gaza Strip
#Text=Fighting and a heavy exchange of fire between Israel and Hamas continued in the Gaza Strip overnight despite Hamas agreeing to the main outlines of a ceasefire brokered by officials in Egypt .
#Text=On Ramattan ' s live video feed of the strip , Israeli tanks and gunships could be seen continuing to strike their targets , while Hamas fought Israeli soldiers on the streets .
#Text=This marks the third night of intense bombings and exchanges .
#Text=The fighting has brought the Palestinian death toll from the Israeli offensive to over 1,000 , leaving thousands more injured .
#Text=" [ We ] presented to the Egyptian leadership our detailed vision , " said Hamas in a statement which also added that Hamas did not reject the proposal .
#Text=The Israeli government is said to be looking at details of Hamas 's proposal , but so far no agreement has been reached between the two sides .
#Text=Damage incurred from the war is estimated to cost Gaza nearly US $ 1.5 billion .
#Text=Sources
#Text=Karin Laub . " Palestinians estimate $ 1.4 billion in damage in Gaza from Israeli assault " — Duluth News Tribune , January 14 , 2009
#Text=Adel Zaanoun .
#Text=" Gaza toll passes 1000 as peace hopes rise " — The Australian , January 14 , 2009
#Text=LIVE video feed of Gaza Strip
#Text=Ramattan News Agency
#Text=( Retrieved on January 14 , 2009 ; 6:30 p.m. { EST } )
#Text=Osama bin Laden calls for a violent jihad against Israel
#Text=Osama bin Laden ( file photo )
#Text=The leader of al-Qaeda , Osama bin Laden has released a new audio tape calling for a " holy war " against Israel for their offensive against the Gaza Strip in Palestine .
#Text=The message appeared on Islamist extremist websites in the overnight hours .
#Text=Bin Laden 's message has yet to be verified by intelligence officials in the United States , but reports say the voice on the tape is similar to previous recording released by bin Laden .
#Text=In the tape , he calls on Palestinians to engage in a jihad against Israel to " stop the aggression against Gaza " and " liberate Palestine .
